('Stone Fence','["2 oz Rye, bourbon, rum or brandy","1 dash Angostura bitters","Apple cider"]','["Add the spirit and bitters to a Collins glass over ice.","Fill the glass to the brim with the cider and stir.","Garnish with a mint sprig."]','["Mint sprig"]','["collins glass"]'),
