('Manhattan','["2 oz Bourbon","1 oz Carpano Antica Formula vermouth","2 dashes Fee Brothers whiskey-barrel-aged bitters"]','["Add all the ingredients to a mixing glass with ice and stir until exceedingly well-chilled.","Strain into a chilled coupe glass.","Garnish with a lemon twist."]','["Lemon twist"]','["coupe glass"]'),
