('Backyard Iced Tea','["2 oz Spiced rum","1 oz Unsweetened iced tea","2 oz Lemonade"]','["Add all the ingredients to a highball glass filled with ice.","Garnish with a lemon wedge."]','["1 Lemon wedge"]','["highball glass"]'),
