('Kentucky Mule','["2 oz Woodford Reserve bourbon",".5 oz Fresh lime juice","Ginger beer, to top"]','["Add the bourbon and lime juice to a Moscow Mule mug or a highball glass.","Fill the mug or glass with ice and top with ginger beer.","Add mint sprigs for garnish."]','["Mint sprigs"]','["highball glass"]'),
