('Vesper','["3 oz Gin","1 oz Vodka",".5 oz Lillet blanc apéritif"]','["Add all the ingredients into a mixing glass with ice and stir (or, if preparing the Bond way, shake).","Strain into a chilled cocktail glass.","Twist a slice of lemon peel over the drink, rub along the rim of the glass, and drop it in."]','["Lemon twist"]','["cocktail glass"]'),
