('Long Zest','["2 oz Glenmorangie Original scotch","3 dashes Angostura bitters","Fever-Tree ginger ale"]','["Add the scotch and bitters into a rocks glass over ice, and stir.","Top with the ginger ale, flame an orange peel to express the oils, then add as a garnish."]','["Flamed orange peel"]','["rocks glass"]'),
