('Cupid''s Champagne Potion','["1 oz Belvedere vodka","1 oz Peach puree","Veuve Clicquot Yellow Label Champagne"]','["Add the vodka and peach puree into a shaker and fill with ice, and shake until chilled.","Strain into a chilled Champagne flute.","Top with Champagne."]','[]','["champagne flute"]'),
