('The Murphy Sour','["1 tbsp Chopped fresh Cilantro leaves","1 Clementine, peeled","1.5 oz Campo de Encanto Acholado Pisco",".5 oz Lime juice","1 oz Clover honey syrup (one part clover honey, one part water)","1 oz Egg white (or 1 egg white)"]','["In a shaker, muddle the cilantro and clementine.","Add the remaining ingredients and shake without ice for 5 seconds.","Fill with ice and shake well.","Double-strain into a cocktail glass and garnish with a cilantro sprig."]','["1 Cilantro sprig"]','["cocktail glass"]'),
