('Maxwell','["1.5 oz Square One cucumber vodka",".75 oz Cucumber juice",".25 oz Cointreau",".5 oz Lemon juice",".25 oz Agave nectar","187 ml Brut Champagne or other sparkling wine (about 1 split bottle)"]','["Serves 2.","Add all ingredients except Champagne into a large shaker with ice and shake well for 10 seconds.","Double-strain into 2 flutes.","Top each with Champagne and chill the rest of the bottle in an ice bucket.","While drinking, top with more Champagne as needed."]','[]','["flute"]'),
